00:17:17,859 --> 00:17:18,700
[SPEAKER_00] s pozornice,

397
00:17:18,700 --> 00:17:20,660
[SPEAKER_00] ako Isusa stavimo,

398
00:17:20,660 --> 00:17:22,579
[SPEAKER_00] čuda će bit.

399
00:17:22,579 --> 00:17:24,180
[SPEAKER_00] Nama čuda

400
00:17:24,180 --> 00:17:24,920
[SPEAKER_00] danas trebaju

401
00:17:24,920 --> 00:17:25,420
[SPEAKER_00] više nego

402
00:17:25,420 --> 00:17:25,859
[SPEAKER_00] ikada.

403
00:17:25,859 --> 00:17:27,859
[SPEAKER_00] Nisam ona osoba

404
00:17:27,859 --> 00:17:28,680
[SPEAKER_00] koja navještaj

405
00:17:28,680 --> 00:17:29,900
[SPEAKER_00] govori o emocijama,

406
00:17:29,900 --> 00:17:31,059
[SPEAKER_00] o tim slatkim

407
00:17:31,059 --> 00:17:31,740
[SPEAKER_00] trenucima,

408
00:17:31,740 --> 00:17:32,160
[SPEAKER_00] ne znam,

409
00:17:32,279 --> 00:17:33,079
[SPEAKER_00] svi smo ih prošli

410
00:17:33,079 --> 00:17:33,839
[SPEAKER_00] kod obraćenja

411
00:17:33,839 --> 00:17:34,519
[SPEAKER_00] i to je super.

412
00:17:35,599 --> 00:17:36,460
[SPEAKER_00] ali nam trebaju

413
00:17:36,460 --> 00:17:37,400
[SPEAKER_00] čuda u crkvi,

414
00:17:37,400 --> 00:17:38,779
[SPEAKER_00] trebaju nam čuda

415
00:17:38,779 --> 00:17:39,680
[SPEAKER_00] u našoj vjeri

416
00:17:39,680 --> 00:17:40,839
[SPEAKER_00] da odjekne,

417
00:17:40,839 --> 00:17:42,079
[SPEAKER_00] da odjekne

418
00:17:42,079 --> 00:17:42,960
[SPEAKER_00] da je Isus živ,

419
00:17:42,960 --> 00:17:44,480
[SPEAKER_00] da odjekne,

420
00:17:44,480 --> 00:17:45,019
[SPEAKER_00] da se zna,

421
00:17:45,019 --> 00:17:45,839
[SPEAKER_00] da se priča,

422
00:17:45,839 --> 00:17:46,980
[SPEAKER_00] da se prepričava.

423
00:17:46,980 --> 00:17:49,900
[SPEAKER_00] I pogledajte,

424
00:17:49,900 --> 00:17:51,660
[SPEAKER_00] kad se i obratiš

425
00:17:51,660 --> 00:17:52,539
[SPEAKER_00] i doživiš nešto

426
00:17:52,539 --> 00:17:53,339
[SPEAKER_00] da je Bog živ,

427
00:17:53,339 --> 00:17:55,099
[SPEAKER_00] kad ti otvori srce

428
00:17:55,099 --> 00:17:56,160
[SPEAKER_00] i to pričaš drugima,

429
00:17:56,160 --> 00:17:57,720
[SPEAKER_00] u istoj obitelji

430
00:17:57,720 --> 00:17:58,619
[SPEAKER_00] u kojoj živiš,

431
00:17:58,619 --> 00:18:00,220
[SPEAKER_00] smiju ti se u facu,

432
00:18:01,099 --> 00:18:02,299
[SPEAKER_00] nemoj pretjerivati

433
00:18:02,299 --> 00:18:04,019
[SPEAKER_00] jesi poludio,

434
00:18:04,019 --> 00:18:05,980
[SPEAKER_00] šta ćeš svaki četvrtak gore,

435
00:18:05,980 --> 00:18:07,299
[SPEAKER_00] s tobom nešto nije u redu.

436
00:18:07,299 --> 00:18:09,779
[SPEAKER_00] Vi mladi to dobro znate

437
00:18:09,779 --> 00:18:10,940
[SPEAKER_00] kad objavite storij

438
00:18:10,940 --> 00:18:11,819
[SPEAKER_00] iz ovoga mjesta

439
00:18:11,819 --> 00:18:13,380
[SPEAKER_00] ili nekog drugog mjesta

440
00:18:13,380 --> 00:18:15,440
[SPEAKER_00] vjerskoga,

441
00:18:15,440 --> 00:18:16,920
[SPEAKER_00] pa kako vas nevi smijavati.

442
00:18:16,920 --> 00:18:19,799
[SPEAKER_00] Vi nji nemojte ismijavati,

443
00:18:19,799 --> 00:18:21,859
[SPEAKER_00] vi nji mažite ljubavlju,

444
00:18:21,859 --> 00:18:24,559
[SPEAKER_00] pomažite i milošću Božjema

445
00:18:24,559 --> 00:18:26,440
[SPEAKER_00] autoritetom Isusa Krista,

446
00:18:26,440 --> 00:18:28,759
[SPEAKER_00] zazovi krv Isusa Krista

447
00:18:28,759 --> 00:18:29,599
[SPEAKER_00] na sve njih,

448
00:18:30,319 --> 00:18:31,299
[SPEAKER_00] nikada ne mrzi,

449
00:18:31,299 --> 00:18:34,619
[SPEAKER_00] ljubi i moli autoritetom.

450
00:18:34,619 --> 00:18:37,319
[SPEAKER_00] Neka se i oni obrate,

451
00:18:37,319 --> 00:18:40,180
[SPEAKER_00] neka se i njihovo srce otvori.

452
00:18:40,180 --> 00:18:41,680
[SPEAKER_00] Možda je i neko

453
00:18:41,680 --> 00:18:43,680
[SPEAKER_00] i za moje i tvoje srce molio.

454
00:18:43,680 --> 00:18:46,579
[SPEAKER_00] I mi danas zahvalimo Bogu

455
00:18:46,579 --> 00:18:48,299
[SPEAKER_00] što smo možda doživjeli

456
00:18:48,299 --> 00:18:49,319
[SPEAKER_00] da nas je gospodin dotaknuo,

457
00:18:49,319 --> 00:18:51,839
[SPEAKER_00] da smo doživjeli neko čudo

458
00:18:51,839 --> 00:18:53,799
[SPEAKER_00] i da znamo Isuse živ.

459
00:18:53,799 --> 00:18:58,079
[SPEAKER_00] Crkva će se moći osloniti

460
00:18:58,079 --> 00:18:59,539
[SPEAKER_00] na one koji vjeruju u to,

461
00:18:59,539 --> 00:19:02,200
[SPEAKER_00] a oni koji vjeruju samo u svoj

462
00:19:02,200 --> 00:19:03,559
[SPEAKER_00] suhi, ljudski

463
00:19:03,559 --> 00:19:05,920
[SPEAKER_00] nauk,

464
00:19:05,920 --> 00:19:07,400
[SPEAKER_00] izlaganje,

465
00:19:07,400 --> 00:19:09,160
[SPEAKER_00] bez pomazanja i čuda,

466
00:19:09,160 --> 00:19:11,680
[SPEAKER_00] njima je teško.

467
00:19:12,779 --> 00:19:14,880
[SPEAKER_00] pogledajte stanje crke u Evropi.

468
00:19:14,880 --> 00:19:17,940
[SPEAKER_00] Ja često sam tamo i više puta to spominje.

469
00:19:17,940 --> 00:19:21,660
[SPEAKER_00] Pa uopće se ne čudim da se zatvara na nekim mjestima.

470
00:19:23,799 --> 00:19:24,960
[SPEAKER_00] uopće se ne čudim.

471
00:19:24,960 --> 00:19:29,579
[SPEAKER_00] Zatvara se zato što je se Boga potisnulo.

472
00:19:30,779 --> 00:19:32,759
[SPEAKER_00] E sad, ja sam krenio sa hramom.

473
00:19:34,440 --> 00:19:40,099
[SPEAKER_00] Hram je bio i sa svim tim farizejima i pismoznancima koji su teoreski sve znali.

474
00:19:42,099 --> 00:19:44,660
[SPEAKER_00] Hram se promijenio kada je Isus unišao

475
00:19:44,660 --> 00:19:46,519
[SPEAKER_00] u taj hram.

476
00:19:46,519 --> 00:19:48,319
[SPEAKER_00] Što je tada započelo?

477
00:19:48,319 --> 00:19:49,759
[SPEAKER_00] Upravo ovim.

478
00:19:49,759 --> 00:19:53,980
[SPEAKER_00] Njegovo očitovanje i milost i snaga kraljevstva Božjega.

479
00:19:55,039 --> 00:19:57,480
[SPEAKER_00] Do tada su ljudi živjeli u grijehu, u robstvu.

480
00:19:57,480 --> 00:20:00,539
[SPEAKER_00] Isus nastupa, donosi ozdravljenje.

481
00:20:00,539 --> 00:20:03,440
[SPEAKER_00] Istjeruje, oslobađa, obsjednutoga.

482
00:20:03,440 --> 00:20:05,279
[SPEAKER_00] Praštaju se grijesi.

483
00:20:05,279 --> 00:20:13,059
[SPEAKER_00] I to je nacrt koji je Isus u sinagogi započeo da bude i u crkvi.

484
00:20:13,059 --> 00:20:19,099
[SPEAKER_00] I bit će u crkvi uvijek tako ako se budemo držali plana Isusovog.

485
00:20:19,099 --> 00:20:24,799
[SPEAKER_00] Ako mi u crkvi ostupimo od Isusovog plana i ne budemo bili vjerni njemu,

486
00:20:25,039 --> 00:20:28,559
[SPEAKER_00] i da navještamo bez svog interesa,

487
00:20:28,559 --> 00:20:31,000
[SPEAKER_00] gospodin će se proslavljati.

488
00:20:31,000 --> 00:20:32,339
[SPEAKER_00] Crkve će biti pune.

489
00:20:32,339 --> 00:20:35,980
[SPEAKER_00] Tamo gdje smo zatvorili uši na njegov nauk,

490
00:20:35,980 --> 00:20:39,720
[SPEAKER_00] tamo gdje smo njegove istine počeli relativizirati

491
00:20:39,720 --> 00:20:42,880
[SPEAKER_00] i stavljati sebe na prvo mjesto,

492
00:20:42,880 --> 00:20:45,359
[SPEAKER_00] tamo se crkve i zatvaraju.

493
00:20:45,359 --> 00:20:49,500
[SPEAKER_00] Koliki pokušaj nekakvih reformi?

494
00:20:49,500 --> 00:20:53,119
[SPEAKER_00] Koliki pokušaj nekakve promjene stanja crkve?

495
00:20:54,700 --> 00:20:57,920
[SPEAKER_00] Niko ne priča o ovom autoritetu i milosti duha svetoga,

496
00:20:57,920 --> 00:21:00,980
[SPEAKER_00] što ćemo mi to, mi smo eksperti da promijenimo crkvu.

497
00:21:00,980 --> 00:21:05,099
[SPEAKER_00] Jesmo mi to stvarno eksperti da nekom zapalimo srce ili duh sveti?

498
00:21:05,099 --> 00:21:10,940
[SPEAKER_00] E ta nam vjera treba.

499
00:21:10,940 --> 00:21:13,940
[SPEAKER_00] Jer što se može dogoditi našoj crkvi,

500
00:21:13,940 --> 00:21:16,940
[SPEAKER_00] kao i onog trenutka kad je Isus bio u sinagogi?

501
00:21:18,700 --> 00:21:24,460
[SPEAKER_00] Jer gledajte, u sinagogi, gdje su bili pismo znanci,

502
00:21:24,460 --> 00:21:30,460
[SPEAKER_00] nije smetalo džavu, nije se manifestirao u onome bolesniku

503
00:21:30,460 --> 00:21:34,960
[SPEAKER_00] kad je susreo pismo znance, već kad je susreo Isusa.

504
00:21:35,960 --> 00:21:38,839
[SPEAKER_00] Jer ako si i mi ne budemo vjerni Božjoj riječi,

505
00:21:38,839 --> 00:21:41,819
[SPEAKER_00] u poniznosti, i vjerovali ono što on kaže,

506
00:21:41,819 --> 00:21:44,099
[SPEAKER_00] i vjerovali njegovo poslanje,

507
00:21:44,099 --> 00:21:45,720
[SPEAKER_00] nama će se dogoditi isto.

508
00:21:48,359 --> 00:21:51,720
[SPEAKER_00] Kako je, to je jedan egzorcista lijepo objasnio,

509
00:21:51,720 --> 00:21:53,680
[SPEAKER_00] kad je mu neko postavio pitanje,

510
00:21:53,680 --> 00:21:57,660
[SPEAKER_00] kako to da se demoni mogu očitovati u crkvi?

511
00:21:57,660 --> 00:22:02,220
[SPEAKER_00] A onda on odgovorio, pa zato što tamo mnogi nemaju vjere.

512
00:22:02,220 --> 00:22:05,579
[SPEAKER_00] Mnogi nemaju vjere.

513
00:22:05,579 --> 00:22:08,640
[SPEAKER_00] Mnogi ljudi danas su kršteni,

514
00:22:08,640 --> 00:22:10,819
[SPEAKER_00] ljudi, ali nemaju iskustvo živog Boga.

515
00:22:10,819 --> 00:22:14,539
[SPEAKER_00] I umriće tako, u neznanju,

516
00:22:15,599 --> 00:22:16,839
[SPEAKER_00] a mi ne snijemo šuditi.

517
00:22:16,839 --> 00:22:19,980
[SPEAKER_00] Makar nije danas zgodno propovijedati.

518
00:22:19,980 --> 00:22:24,200
[SPEAKER_00] Nije zgodno biti otvoreni reći kako stvari stoje.

519
00:22:24,200 --> 00:22:27,640
[SPEAKER_00] Ali, je li nas gospodin izabrao

520
00:22:27,640 --> 00:22:30,480
[SPEAKER_00] da udovoljavamo mišljenjima drugih

521
00:22:30,480 --> 00:22:33,400
[SPEAKER_00] ili da se držimo njegovog autoriteta?

522
00:22:33,400 --> 00:22:36,839
[SPEAKER_00] Jer ako nas Isus pozvao

523
00:22:36,839 --> 00:22:39,079
[SPEAKER_00] i ove koje je dvanestorice pozvao,

524
00:22:39,079 --> 00:22:40,559
[SPEAKER_00] šalje i da idu bez ičega,

525
00:22:40,559 --> 00:22:42,720
[SPEAKER_00] imali su pravo da mu prigovaraju.

526
00:22:42,720 --> 00:22:43,539
[SPEAKER_00] Sli normalan?

527
00:22:43,900 --> 00:22:45,400
[SPEAKER_00] Bez kruha, da idemo bez odjeće,

528
00:22:45,400 --> 00:22:46,640
[SPEAKER_00] bez štapa, bez ičega.

529
00:22:46,640 --> 00:22:49,640
[SPEAKER_00] Danas te pitam jedno.

530
00:22:49,640 --> 00:22:52,160
[SPEAKER_00] Ili ćeš gospodinu prigovarati stalno

531
00:22:52,160 --> 00:22:54,180
[SPEAKER_00] kad te šalje u određene uvjete

532
00:22:54,180 --> 00:22:55,779
[SPEAKER_00] ili ćeš samo ići?

533
00:22:55,779 --> 00:22:56,920
[SPEAKER_00] Ne ima druge opcije.

534
00:22:56,920 --> 00:22:59,980
[SPEAKER_00] Mi imamo danas više one koji Bogu prigovaraju

535
00:22:59,980 --> 00:23:01,380
[SPEAKER_00] kad išalje ili kad Bogu pokušaju

536
00:23:01,380 --> 00:23:02,519
[SPEAKER_00] preko nas nešto napraviti.

537
00:23:02,519 --> 00:23:04,819
[SPEAKER_00] Mi nađemo sto razloga da prigovaramo

538
00:23:04,819 --> 00:23:06,799
[SPEAKER_00] i ostanemo u našem prigovaranju

539
00:23:06,799 --> 00:23:08,559
[SPEAKER_00] umjesto samo da odemo i da napravimo.

540
00:23:08,960 --> 00:23:09,859
[SPEAKER_00] Da se oslonimo.

541
00:23:09,859 --> 00:23:14,519
[SPEAKER_00] Ovi sučenici sve to mogli reći nijemu.

542
00:23:14,519 --> 00:23:16,859
[SPEAKER_00] Do ja nećično, još me tako slati nesigurnost,

543
00:23:16,859 --> 00:23:17,500
[SPEAKER_00] tako onako.

544
00:23:20,079 --> 00:23:22,299
[SPEAKER_00] E to nam treba pouzdanju Božiju riječ.

545
00:23:22,299 --> 00:23:23,640
[SPEAKER_00] I onda se ne treba bojati.

546
00:23:23,640 --> 00:23:24,519
[SPEAKER_00] Bog će činiti.

547
00:23:24,519 --> 00:23:27,359
[SPEAKER_00] Jer Bogu je stalo više

548
00:23:27,359 --> 00:23:29,119
[SPEAKER_00] do ljudi nego

549
00:23:29,119 --> 00:23:30,900
[SPEAKER_00] što mi možda možemo

550
00:23:30,900 --> 00:23:32,279
[SPEAKER_00] i zamisliti.

551
00:23:32,279 --> 00:23:34,200
[SPEAKER_00] Zato, dragi mladi,

552
00:23:34,200 --> 00:23:37,019
[SPEAKER_00] vi ste veliki instrument u Božim rukama.

553
00:23:37,019 --> 00:23:39,420
[SPEAKER_00] Znam da mnogi mislite, ja sam samo lajk,

554
00:23:39,420 --> 00:23:40,819
[SPEAKER_00] ja ne znam ništa.

555
00:23:40,819 --> 00:23:44,059
[SPEAKER_00] Meni što je bitno,

556
00:23:44,059 --> 00:23:46,180
[SPEAKER_00] da ti imaš iskustvo Boga.

557
00:23:47,200 --> 00:23:48,960
[SPEAKER_00] Jer ćeš ti onda nećeš šutiti,

558
00:23:48,960 --> 00:23:49,880
[SPEAKER_00] već ćeš pričati.

559
00:23:49,880 --> 00:23:52,559
[SPEAKER_00] Ja puno puta ovako,

560
00:23:52,559 --> 00:23:54,680
[SPEAKER_00] kad vas pokušavam animirati za nešto,

561
00:23:54,680 --> 00:23:55,960
[SPEAKER_00] da pomognete u crkvi

562
00:23:55,960 --> 00:23:57,039
[SPEAKER_00] ili da radite,

563
00:23:57,039 --> 00:23:57,779
[SPEAKER_00] ili svjedočite,

564
00:23:57,779 --> 00:23:59,259
[SPEAKER_00] joj, nemoj pater,

565
00:23:59,259 --> 00:24:00,039
[SPEAKER_00] ja ne znam,

566
00:24:00,039 --> 00:24:01,880
[SPEAKER_00] pa ja bi se trebao tu malo pripremati,

567
00:24:01,880 --> 00:24:04,539
[SPEAKER_00] pa ja bi sad trebao završiti teologiju,

568
00:24:04,539 --> 00:24:05,859
[SPEAKER_00] pa ću onda propovijedati.

569
00:24:05,859 --> 00:24:07,400
[SPEAKER_00] Ja bi on sve to prođe,

570
00:24:07,400 --> 00:24:08,960
[SPEAKER_00] kakve specializacije,

571
00:24:08,960 --> 00:24:10,720
[SPEAKER_00] pa dije onda tu oslanjanje na Boga.

572
00:24:11,220 --> 00:24:13,880
[SPEAKER_00] Naravno da se moramo u znanju nadograđivati,

573
00:24:13,880 --> 00:24:17,480
[SPEAKER_00] ali moramo paziti na što se oslanjamo.

574
00:24:17,480 --> 00:24:20,279
[SPEAKER_00] Što dramiš,

575
00:24:20,279 --> 00:24:21,619
[SPEAKER_00] imaš talent da sviraš,

576
00:24:21,619 --> 00:24:22,579
[SPEAKER_00] ili nešto da radiš,

577
00:24:22,579 --> 00:24:24,420
[SPEAKER_00] ili pjevaš i sve ostalo,

578
00:24:24,420 --> 00:24:26,059
[SPEAKER_00] a ti si i dalje trom, trom.

579
00:24:26,059 --> 00:24:29,660
[SPEAKER_00] Šta Bog može napraviti po tebi,

580
00:24:29,660 --> 00:24:30,839
[SPEAKER_00] po meni ako smo tromi,

581
00:24:30,839 --> 00:24:31,980
[SPEAKER_00] tromi mi svećenici,

582
00:24:31,980 --> 00:24:33,019
[SPEAKER_00] tromi vi lajici,

583
00:24:33,019 --> 00:24:34,079
[SPEAKER_00] šta je ovo?

584
00:24:35,839 --> 00:24:38,299
[SPEAKER_00] Treba otvoriti te prozore što imam Pavel II. kaže

585
00:24:38,299 --> 00:24:41,000
[SPEAKER_00] dajte malo ne produše taj duh sveti

586
00:24:41,000 --> 00:24:42,220
[SPEAKER_00] da nas sve malo trgne.

587
00:24:42,220 --> 00:24:45,299
[SPEAKER_00] Mi trebamo ono katarzu,

588
00:24:45,299 --> 00:24:46,519
[SPEAKER_00] čišćenje duhovno.

589
00:24:46,519 --> 00:24:50,140
[SPEAKER_00] Da mi koji navještamo,

590
00:24:50,140 --> 00:24:51,420
[SPEAKER_00] ne znamo šta navještamo.

591
00:24:51,420 --> 00:24:55,079
[SPEAKER_00] Da mi koji vjerujemo,

592
00:24:55,079 --> 00:24:56,460
[SPEAKER_00] ne imamo žara.

593
00:24:56,460 --> 00:24:58,980
[SPEAKER_00] Sve mi je nešto to kontradiktorno.

594
00:24:58,980 --> 00:25:02,799
[SPEAKER_00] Zato je pred nama velika zadaća.

595
00:25:02,799 --> 00:25:04,900
[SPEAKER_00] Velika odgovornost.

596
00:25:05,480 --> 00:25:07,480
[SPEAKER_00] lakše je prihvatiti mentalitet

597
00:25:07,480 --> 00:25:08,400
[SPEAKER_00] i kritizirati.

598
00:25:08,400 --> 00:25:10,299
[SPEAKER_00] Ništa nije dobro,

599
00:25:10,299 --> 00:25:11,759
[SPEAKER_00] ne valja ništa,

600
00:25:11,759 --> 00:25:13,480
[SPEAKER_00] mislim je ona dosadna,

601
00:25:13,480 --> 00:25:14,920
[SPEAKER_00] ona je pop katastrofa,

602
00:25:14,920 --> 00:25:16,000
[SPEAKER_00] crkva je vaka.

603
00:25:16,000 --> 00:25:18,420
[SPEAKER_00] Brate, šta si ti učinio za tu crkvu?

604
00:25:18,420 --> 00:25:21,339
[SPEAKER_00] Šta je Bog po tebi napravio konkretno?

605
00:25:21,339 --> 00:25:23,099
[SPEAKER_00] Posti ti onog svećenika,

606
00:25:23,099 --> 00:25:25,279
[SPEAKER_00] kakav god da je ono svoju susjedu

607
00:25:25,279 --> 00:25:26,079
[SPEAKER_00] ili ne znam koga.

608
00:25:26,079 --> 00:25:28,660
[SPEAKER_00] Pitam te, šta je Bog po tebi napravio?

609
00:25:28,660 --> 00:25:33,740
[SPEAKER_00] Kome si ti Boga donio?

610
00:25:35,119 --> 00:25:39,839
[SPEAKER_00] E to je zadaća svih nas.

611
00:25:39,839 --> 00:25:41,240
[SPEAKER_00] I ne zaboravimo.

612
00:25:41,240 --> 00:25:43,779
[SPEAKER_00] Najljepša je radost

613
00:25:43,779 --> 00:25:45,740
[SPEAKER_00] koju možemo doživiti.

614
00:25:45,740 --> 00:25:46,819
[SPEAKER_00] Znam da nekima možda

615
00:25:46,819 --> 00:25:48,579
[SPEAKER_00] ovakad razmišljaju

616
00:25:48,579 --> 00:25:51,140
[SPEAKER_00] izgleda jako teško

617
00:25:51,140 --> 00:25:51,940
[SPEAKER_00] što mora, ne znam,

618
00:25:51,940 --> 00:25:53,940
[SPEAKER_00] naviještati ili služiti ili ostalo.

619
00:25:54,940 --> 00:25:56,140
[SPEAKER_00] Ne ima veće radosti.

620
00:25:56,140 --> 00:25:58,319
[SPEAKER_00] Ne ima veće radosti.

621
00:25:58,319 --> 00:26:00,579
[SPEAKER_00] Pomoći nekom da otvori srce.

622
00:26:00,579 --> 00:26:04,980
[SPEAKER_00] Pomoći nekom da dođe do iskustva Boga.

623
00:26:04,980 --> 00:26:07,559
[SPEAKER_00] Nema tog znanja

624
00:26:07,559 --> 00:26:09,900
[SPEAKER_00] ili tvoje sposobnosti u životu

625
00:26:09,900 --> 00:26:11,160
[SPEAKER_00] koje možeš napraviti od ove.

626
00:26:11,380 --> 00:26:12,420
[SPEAKER_00] To je tako lijepo.

627
00:26:12,420 --> 00:26:13,559
[SPEAKER_00] To je tako dobro

628
00:26:13,559 --> 00:26:15,880
[SPEAKER_00] i za tebe i za drugi.

629
00:26:15,880 --> 00:26:17,940
[SPEAKER_00] Evo, molimo gospodina

630
00:26:17,940 --> 00:26:19,740
[SPEAKER_00] da zaista prihvatimo

631
00:26:19,740 --> 00:26:22,019
[SPEAKER_00] onaj autoritet koji od njega dolazi.

632
00:26:22,019 --> 00:26:23,559
[SPEAKER_00] Da, znam,

633
00:26:23,559 --> 00:26:25,960
[SPEAKER_00] ne mislim da trebamo pretjerivati,

634
00:26:25,960 --> 00:26:28,200
[SPEAKER_00] ne mislim da se trebamo umišljati,

635
00:26:28,700 --> 00:26:29,700
[SPEAKER_00] ali ne živcira

636
00:26:29,700 --> 00:26:31,759
[SPEAKER_00] kad smo obezhrabreni.

637
00:26:31,759 --> 00:26:33,940
[SPEAKER_00] Živcira nekad pričamo

638
00:26:33,940 --> 00:26:35,160
[SPEAKER_00] o budućnosti crkve,

639
00:26:35,160 --> 00:26:36,279
[SPEAKER_00] o vjeri, o zvanjima

640
00:26:36,279 --> 00:26:37,599
[SPEAKER_00] kao da Boga nema.

641
00:26:37,599 --> 00:26:39,099
[SPEAKER_00] Kao da zvanja duhovna

642
00:26:39,099 --> 00:26:39,940
[SPEAKER_00] ovi se omeni.

643
00:26:39,940 --> 00:26:41,240
[SPEAKER_00] Moje je da radim,

644
00:26:41,240 --> 00:26:42,859
[SPEAKER_00] da molim i Bog će poslati.

645
00:26:42,859 --> 00:26:47,519
[SPEAKER_00] I stalno nešto govorimo,

646
00:26:47,519 --> 00:26:48,519
[SPEAKER_00] gunđamo, gunđamo,

647
00:26:48,519 --> 00:26:49,460
[SPEAKER_00] ništa ne činimo.

648
00:26:49,460 --> 00:26:50,759
[SPEAKER_00] Evo, to mi je žao.

649
00:26:50,759 --> 00:26:53,680
[SPEAKER_00] Ajmo se ohrabriti.

650
00:26:53,680 --> 00:26:54,859
[SPEAKER_00] Ajmo moliti već raz

651
00:26:54,859 --> 00:26:56,660
[SPEAKER_00] za to pomazanje duha svetoga

652
00:26:56,660 --> 00:26:58,200
[SPEAKER_00] da zaista gorimo svi,

653
00:26:58,279 --> 00:26:59,779
[SPEAKER_00] da si počne ugljati pozitivno.

654
00:26:59,779 --> 00:27:01,759
[SPEAKER_00] Ej, pa ja mogu ovoj crkvi pomoći.

655
00:27:01,759 --> 00:27:03,500
[SPEAKER_00] Ne crkvi kao instituci.

656
00:27:03,500 --> 00:27:06,559
[SPEAKER_00] Kristu mogu pomoći na ovaj način.

657
00:27:06,559 --> 00:27:08,059
[SPEAKER_00] Daj mi, gospodine,

658
00:27:08,059 --> 00:27:09,059
[SPEAKER_00] tu vatru i žar.

659
00:27:09,059 --> 00:27:11,359
[SPEAKER_00] Pomazanje da ja tebe svjedočim

660
00:27:11,359 --> 00:27:13,160
[SPEAKER_00] zaista onakako s ti obeću.

661
00:27:13,160 --> 00:27:14,359
[SPEAKER_00] Dje ti to mene zoveš?

662
00:27:14,359 --> 00:27:17,000
[SPEAKER_00] Šalji me tamo gdje hoćeš

663
00:27:17,000 --> 00:27:18,799
[SPEAKER_00] sa svojim autoritetom.

664
00:27:18,799 --> 00:27:19,200
[SPEAKER_00] Amen.

